test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 0 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ded04b96540>([13])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ded04b96540> = [[13], [13, 1], [13], [13, 1], [13], []].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ded04b96540>([1, 13])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ded04b96540> = [[13], [13, 1], [13], [13, 1], [13], []].count

assert 1 == 13
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
